GEN 1.31 Ke God keniaw re o tartar pene yi na ko, ke re koro omon peyian.|src="co00604b.TIF" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="1.31" captionR="God i lukim olgeta samting em i bin wokim na ol i gutpela tru." refR="1.31" srcref="GEN 1.31"
GEN 2.25 Tem soene niy wuruaw ro temiyn ene karwa eliro peyian, elinke eliro elin kemyiey ro.|src="co00603b.tif" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="2.25" captionR="Long dispela taim man wantaim meri hia i raun skin nating, tasol tupela i no pilim sem." refR="2.25" srcref="GEN 2.25"
GEN 3.7 Ro karaimana re aiy fik roiyn ono ko pene roiyn iyn ro kelꞌieytekna ro.|src="CO00609B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="3.7" captionR="Tupela i samapim ol lip bilong diwai fik i kamap olsem laplap we tupela ken pasim na haitim bodi bilong tupela." refR="3.7" srcref="GEN 3.7"
GEN 3.24 Re koro pasin kokelek, peneke God kawpaij niy lamat ene karwa wum lilin.|src="CO00610B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="3.24" captionR="Ol i mekim sin, olsem na God i rausim ol i go autsait long gaden." refR="3.24" srcref="GEN 3.24"
GEN 4.8 Kein ono kala wanan totot Abel ono kamat.|src="CO00617B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="4.8" captionR="Kein i kilim liklik brata bilong em Abel i dai." refR="4.8" srcref="GEN 4.8"
GEN 6.21 God kes Noa, E mas aktiey re aiy omon omon ke awkuo wuak taako.|src="CO00625B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="6.14" captionR="God i tokim Noa, Yu mas kisim ol gutpela gutpela diwai na wokim wanpela sip." refR="6.14" srcref="GEN 6.21"
GEN 7.12 Wus prum ektek kos waꞌiw teriey ene kawa kospaijna araw 40-pla ke puiyn 40-pla.|src="CO00628B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="7.12" captionR="Bikpela ren moa i kam daun long graun, long de na long nait, i stap inap 40-pela de na 40-pela nait." refR="7.12" srcref="GEN 7.12"
GEN 8.19 Noa ke re niy yiꞌe ke re o amaw tartar ono karwa lilin.|src="CO00634B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="8.18" captionR="Noa wantaim ol lain bilong em, na olgeta animal, i go autsait long sip." refR="8.18" srcref="GEN 8.19"
GEN 9.16 God kes pene, Emkoiy ene awmen pene mak iyn kontrak ya kuo kawa na re o tartar iyn teriey ene.|src="CO00636b.tif" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="9.13" captionR="God i tok, Dispela renbo bai i stap olsem mak bilong kontrak mi mekim wantaim olgeta samting bilong graun." refR="9.13" srcref="GEN 9.16"
GEN 11.4 Re niy keres pene, Et mas ato aimol prum ektekma etpe ete. Aimol prum joene awꞌep tawa teken taako ke awaꞌa wa awꞌeptawa teiynjieiyn eyiat ono.|src="CO00638B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="11.4" captionR="Ol man i tok, Yumi mas wokim bikpela taun bilong yumi yet. Dispela bikpela taun bai i gat wanpela longpela tawa bai i go antap tru na tatsim skai antap hia" refR="11.4" srcref="GEN 11.4"
GEN 12.5 Abram koꞌo owuan temiyn yiꞌe Sarai ono ke niꞌin totot yiꞌe Lot, ke re niy yi'e ke re o tartar yi'e ke re karwa iyn arwa teriey iyn Kenan.|src="CO00642B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="12.5" captionR="Abram i kisim meri bilong em Sarai na liklik kandre bilong em Lot, na ol lain bilong em na olgeta samting bilong em na ol i go long graun Kenan." refR="12.5" srcref="GEN 12.5"
GEN 13.9 Abram kes Lot pene, Teriey prum ektek akmen soono. Ekniaw ke akꞌiep on iyn e wua akmin ke on yape awꞌiep iyn ya awmin.|src="CO00647b.tif" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="13.9" captionR="Abraham i tokim Lot olsem, Bikpela hap graun i stap. Yu yet skelim na wanem hap yu makim long go stap long en, orait mi tu bai stap long hap bilong en." refR="13.9" srcref="GEN 13.9"
GEN 18.12 Sara kemen toklontekna re aij.|src="CO00655B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="18.10" captionR="Sara i wok long harim toktok bilong ol." refR="18.10" srcref="GEN 18.12"
GEN 19.8 Lot koto notawtaon yiꞌe lilin.|src="CO00651b.tif" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="19.8" captionR="Lot i sanap long dua bilong em." refR="19.8" srcref="GEN 19.8"
GEN 22.9 Abraham koꞌana Aisak kon aiy yi na eiyliw akto alta onima ono.|src="CO00663b.tif" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="22.9" captionR="Abraham i slipim Isak antap long ol paiawut em i bin lainim antap long alta." refR="22.9" srcref="GEN 22.9"
GEN 24.16 Niy toko Abraham moiyl ono okto tekꞌestek ke Rebeka wama.|src="CO00668B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="24.15" captionR="Wokman bilong Abraham i wok long beten i stap, na Rebeka i kam." refR="24.15" srcref="GEN 24.16"
GEN 25.33 Iso ko promis iyn yi kej namba yiꞌe iyn tonuoiyn watan soono kawa wanan totot yiꞌe Jekop.|src="CO00674B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="25.33" captionR="Iso tok promis long givim namba bilong em i go long liklik brata bilong em Jekop." refR="25.33" srcref="GEN 25.33"
GEN 27.29 Jekop ko blesim Aisak.|src="CO00679B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="27.29" captionR="Jekop i blesim Aaisak." refR="27.29" srcref="GEN 27.29"
GEN 28.15 Tem Aisak kon muoiyn yi kon keniaw pene es taako, remien yiꞌe okto teriey ke noꞌuan yiꞌe waꞌa eyiat heven.|src="CO00683b.tif" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="28.12" captionR="Taim em i slip, Jekop i lukim wanpela driman. Em i lukim wanpela lata, as bilong en i stap long graun na het bilong en i go antap long heven." refR="28.12" srcref="GEN 28.15"
GEN 29.12 Tem Jekop keniaw Resel ke yi akaina at kon raiyn ropuon.|src="CO00687B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="29.10" captionR="Taim Jekop i lukim Resel, em i rausim ston i pasim maus bilong hulwara." refR="29.10" srcref="GEN 29.12"
GEN 31.9 Jekop ke Resel kes Lia pene yi aw'epesie taman yaro ke yi awa enian notaw yi'e.|src="CO00692B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="31.5" captionR="Jekop i tokim Resel na Lia olsem, em i laik lusim papa bilong tupela na go bek long asples bilong em." refR="31.5" srcref="GEN 31.9"
GEN 32.25 Niy taako wama na Jekop ke ro koryuiyn wa kospaijna nian tawtaw.|src="CO00686B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="32.24" captionR="Wanpela man i kam na pait wantaim Jekop i go inap tulait." refR="32.24" srcref="GEN 32.25"
GEN 33.4 Iso kepe wama ke naipem wanan yiꞌe ke muliey yi ke ro kartaiyn ro elen utup peyian.|src="CO00693B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="33.4" captionR="Iso i ran i kam long brata bilong em Jekop na holim pasim em" refR="33.4" srcref="GEN 33.4"
GEN 37.24 Ke re kerleꞌiw Josep waꞌiw wa koto raiyn ropuon kamlan ono epin.|src="CO00705B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="37.24" captionR="Ol i holim Josep na tromoi em i go daun i stap long wanpela hul wara i drai pinis." refR="37.24" srcref="GEN 37.24"
GEN 39.7 Potifa owuan temiyn ono eten tona Josep ke yi tekes yi pene, Ewkuama aktuoiyltuoiyl yia awkuon.|src="CO00716B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="39.7" captionR="Meri bilong Potifar i laikim tru Josep na i tokim em olsem, Yu kam slip wantaim mi." refR="39.7" srcref="GEN 39.7"
