GEN 44.13 Niy toko Josep moiyl keniaw kap iyn Josep'e kemen bek iyn Benjamin.|src="CO00749B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="44.13" captionR="Wokman bilong Josep i lukim kap bilong Josep i stap insait long bek bilong Benjamin." refR="44.13" srcref="GEN 44.13"
