RUT 2.7 Niy takwa watan na moiyl ono kes Boas pene, Niy temiyn soene iyn taw onoo on taako. Yi kataiyl Naomi ro kerꞌepesie kantri Moap ono ke ro karama.|src="co00964b.TIF" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="2.7" srcref="RUT 2.7"
RUT 3.8 Puiyn oluan Boas tapala ke anun kurna yi tem yi keniaw niy temiyn kon tiytiyna yi tewien.|src="co00970b.TIF" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="3.8" srcref="RUT 3.8"
RUT 4.8 Niy soono tekesweyie Boas ono enian pene, Ena awkum teriey on soono. Ke yi terpaij su yiꞌe ono ke yi kej Boas.|src="co00971b.TIF" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="4.8" srcref="RUT 4.8"
RUT 4.17 Re temiyn iyn taw soono teres pene, Naomi ono keꞌep tupun wuruaw.>> Ke re kerkiy yi Obet. Ke epin Obet ono koꞌow Jesi ke Jesi ono koꞌow Devit.|src="co00975b.tif" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="4.17" srcref="RUT 4.17"
MAT 1.25 Josep ko o pene ensel iyn Niy Prumꞌe na kes yi ono ke yi keꞌep Maria ono pene owuan temiyn yiꞌe|src="CN01613b.tif" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="1.25" captionR="Josep i mekim samting olsem ensel bilong Bikpela i bin tokim em na em i kisim Maria na tupela i marit." refR="1.25" srcref="MAT 1.25"
MAT 2.2 Re niy korlon ektek keres pene, Et teniaw amiam yiꞌe kai waꞌa koto, peneke et na tama iyn atꞌestek yi ene.|src="CN01628b.tif" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="2.2" captionR="Ol saveman i tok, Mipela i lukim sta bilong em i go antap, olsem na mipela kam bilong lotu long em." refR="2.2" srcref="MAT 2.2"
MAT 2.12 Re kerej yi gol ke sanra omon ke poura oroiyn kemten.|src="GT00021.tif" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="2.11" captionR="Ol i givim em ol gol na gutpela sanda na pawda i gat naispela smel tru" refR="2.11" srcref="MAT 2.12"
MAT 3.12 Yi awawpala re wit iyn awawpaij re asakaiyl tartar ke yi awꞌeiylmana re wit lamat ono ke awꞌeiylos awto olon wit taako, ke re asakaiyl ono, yi awuiylna eteiyn|src="CN01655b.TIF" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="3.12" captionR="Em i bungim ol pikinini wit long putim insait long wanpela haus wit, na ol pipia, em bai kukim long paia" refR="3.12" srcref="MAT 3.12"
MAT 3.17 Holi Spirit iyn Godꞌe wama waꞌiw na yi pene maiyn paiyl.|src="GT00022.tif" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="3.16" captionR="Holi Spirit bilong God i kamdaun long em olsem wanpela pisin balus" refR="3.16" srcref="MAT 3.17"
MAT 4.22 Prem ektek ro kerꞌepesie pinas ke taman roꞌe ono ke ro karwanan Jisas.|src="CN01682B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="4.22" captionR="Hariap tru tupela i lusim bot wantaim papa bilong ol na tupela i bihainim Jisas." refR="4.22" srcref="MAT 4.22"
MAT 5.1 Jisas meniw kemen ow tenien soono ke re disaipel yiꞌe karama na yi.|src="CN01700B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="5.1" captionR="Jisas i sindaun long sait bilong dispela maunten na ol disaipel bilong em i kam long em." refR="5.1" srcref="MAT 5.1"
MAT 5.42 Pene niy taako awes empema e iyn awkuw yi kago yiꞌe ono taw on tekena pene wan kilomita, awo omon iyn awkuw kago yiꞌe ono akwua on tekena pene tu kilomita.|src="CN01601b.tif" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="5.41" captionR="Sapos wanpela man i bosim yu long karim kago bilong em i go longwe liklik inap long kain olsem wan kilomita, orait yu mas karim kago bilong em i go longwe liklik moa inap long kain olsem tu kilomita" refR="5.41" srcref="MAT 5.42"
MAT 6.8 Tem e akꞌiestek, e mas akwua rum eye ono olonma ke akpiemtekna notawtaon ke akmen akꞌiestek God, Taja eye ekmen taw merew, ke akꞌiestek yi.|src="GT00024.tif" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="6.6" captionR="Taim yu i laik beten, yu i mas go insait long rum bilong yu na pasim dua na beten long God, Papa bilong yu i stap long ples hait, na beten long em." refR="6.6" srcref="MAT 6.8"
MAT 6.27 Tamam ome akmen heven ono tekej re otuow o reꞌe. Elinke omna temiyn wuruaw ana, awtalaꞌa ektekma re maiyn ono|src="GT00023.tif" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="6.26" captionR="Papa bilong yupela long heven yet i save givim kaikai long ol. Tasol yupela manmeri i winim tru ol pisin" refR="6.26" srcref="MAT 6.27"
MAT 7.8 Jisas kes pene, Awkera Taja God ke om awkej o pene om tekera.|src="GT00024.tif" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="7.7" captionR="Askim Papa God na yupela bai kisim samting olsem yupela askim" refR="7.7" srcref="MAT 7.8"
MAT 8.9 Kepten iyn ami kes Jisas pene, E awkis aij peyian ke niy toko moiyl peyian na yia ono elin awo yi omon enian.|src="CN01702B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="8.8" captionR="Kepten bilong ami i tokim Jisas olsem, Yu tok tasol na dispela wokman bilong mi bai i orait gen." refR="8.8" srcref="MAT 8.9"
MAT 8.19 Tisa iyn lo taako wama na yi ke tekes yi pene, Tisa, yane awuanan e taw ampia e akwua|src="CN01744B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="8.19" captionR="Wanpela tisa bilong lo i kam long Jisas na i tokim em olsem, Tisa, mi bai bihainim yu long olgeta hap yu bai go" refR="8.19" srcref="MAT 8.19"
MAT 9.2 Re niy elen koroꞌana niy wuruaw taako opon nakan karmat yi ono kon mat taako ke korouw yi wama na Jisas|src="CN01684B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="9.2" captionR="Sampela lain i karim wanpela man lek han bilong em i dai long wanpela mat na karim em i kam kamap long Jisas" refR="9.2" srcref="MAT 9.2"
MAT 9.17 Re tertijna wain owuaw takaꞌiwna wain puon owuaw ta wain puon ke wain ono arto omon|src="GT00026.tif" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="9.17" captionR="Man i mas putim nupela wain i go insait long nupela wain skin bai wain na wain skin tupela wantaim bai i stap orait" refR="9.17" srcref="MAT 9.17"
MAT 9.38 Jisas komo re niy sule onoo terꞌestek reꞌe ono|src="CN01678B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="9.35" captionR="Jisas i skulim ol manmeri insait long ol haus lotu bilong ol" refR="9.35" srcref="MAT 9.38"
MAT 10.8 Jisas kes re aposel aij ke yi kes re karwa|src="CN01672B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="10.5" captionR="Jisas i givim toksave long ol aposel na em i salim ol i go" refR="10.5" srcref="MAT 10.8"
MAT 11.1 Jisas keswawna gutnius iyn Godꞌe ono re aimol iyn Galili|src="cn01715B.tif" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="11.1" captionR="Jisas i skulim na autim tok bilong God long ol manmeri bilong ol taun insait long Galili" refR="11.1" srcref="MAT 11.1"
MAT 11.30 Plan ya kuana akon om toroepin om ana, ko wesian iyn akterpalaꞌiwna om|src="GT00015.tif" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="11.29" captionR="Dispela palang mi bai putim long sol bilong yu i isi long werim" refR="11.29" srcref="MAT 11.30"
MAT 12.10 Niy taako nakan taako kamat yi ono tekmen taw soono.|src="CN01695B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="12.10" captionR="I gat wanpela man wanpela han bilong em i dai i stap long dispela hap" refR="12.10" srcref="MAT 12.10"
MAT 13.2 Jisas kaiyana kemen pinas taako ekmen raiyn ono ke re temiyn wuruaw tartar peyia ektek ono koron toyiat yin ono|src="CN01705B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="13.2" captionR="Jisas i kalap long wanpela bot i stap antap long wara na i sindaun i stap long en na dispela ol bikpela lain manmeri i stap long nambis" refR="13.2" srcref="MAT 13.2"
MAT 13.9 Yi kuiyl re wit owuan ono kawa wum ono ke elen reꞌe wit owuan ono, wa karla koron tawantan ke maiyn karama ke karꞌaiynjek karꞌaiynpaij re konuiyn.|src="GT00046.tif" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="13.4" captionR="Em i wok long tromoi ol sid i go, na sampela bilong ol dispela sid bilong wit i go na pundaun i stap long rot na ol pisin i kam na kaikaim olgeta." refR="13.4" srcref="MAT 13.9"
MAT 13.27 Re tuptup kokelek ono karama aampia ke karmar na koron wum olonma ono?|src="GT00029.tif" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="13.27" captionR="Ol dispela gras nogut i kam olsem wanem na gro insait long gaden hia?" refR="13.27" srcref="MAT 13.27"
MAT 13.30 Re artot re wit ono ke awrem arwa na olon iyn otuow ono|src="cn02110b.tif" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="13.30" captionR="Ol bai i katim ol wit na karim i go na putim long haus kaikai" refR="13.30" srcref="MAT 13.30"
MAT 13.32 Aiy mastet owuan ene o ontonton peyian.|src="GT00047.tif" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="13.32" captionR="Dispela sid bilong diwai mastet em i liklik tru." refR="13.32" srcref="MAT 13.32"
MAT 13.44 Kingdom iyn heven ono ko pene o omon peyianma taako, re wa kerle tala okon wum taako|src="GT00030.tif" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="13.44" captionR="Kingdom bilong heven i olsem wanpela gutpela samting tru ol i bin haitim insait long wanpela gaden" refR="13.44" srcref="MAT 13.44"
MAT 13.57 Et to sawe pene niy soene, niy iyn toko re olon o ono onton, ke tonuan yiꞌe Maria ono|src="CN01608B.tif" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="13.56" captionR="Mipela i save olsem dispela man, em pikinini bilong dispela kamda man na mama bilong em Maria" refR="13.56" srcref="MAT 13.57"
MAT 14.17 Re keres pene, Et teꞌep piyl entin ke bret 5-pla peyian.|src="GT00094.tif" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="14.17" captionR="Ol i tok, Mipela i gat tupela pis na 5-pela bret tasol." refR="14.17" srcref="MAT 14.17"
MAT 14.21 Jisas epak re bret ono ke yi kej re disaipel yiꞌe ono kerweswesna re temiyn wuruaw tartar ono.|src="CN01718B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="14.19" captionR="Jisas i brukim ol dispela bret na em i givim long ol disaipel bilong em na ol i tilim long olgeta manmeri." refR="14.19" srcref="MAT 14.21"
MAT 15.2 Re Farisi pe re tisa iyn lo elen ono karama na Jisas.|src="CN01724B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="15.1" captionR="Sampela bilong ol Farisi na tisa bilong lo i kamap long Jisas." refR="15.1" srcref="MAT 15.2"
MAT 15.34 Re disaipel iyn Jisas ono teres yi pene, Et teꞌep bret 7-pla ke piyl welen elen.|src="GT00054.tif" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="15.34" captionR="Ol disaipel bilong Jisas i tok, Mipela i gat 7-pela bret na sampela liklik pis." refR="15.34" srcref="MAT 15.34"
MAT 16.15 Jisas tekerweyiema re enian pene, Ke ta omna tekes pene yane inan?|src="CN01725B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="16.15" captionR="Na Jisas i askim ol gen olsem, Na yupela yet i tok mi husait?" refR="16.15" srcref="MAT 16.15"
MAT 17.3 Re kerniaw Moses ro Elaija ono korꞌotalama kartaiyl Jisas ono korto teresresna re aij.|src="CN01728B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="17.3" captionR="Ol i lukim Moses tupela Elaija i kamap nating na sanap toktok wantaim Jisas." refR="17.3" srcref="MAT 17.3"
MAT 17.18 Jisas kaij mas kokelek ono ke mas kokelek ono epesie niy onton ono ke tem soono peyia, niy onton ono, elin ko yi omon enian.|src="CN01730B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="17.18" captionR="Jisas i krosim dispela spirit nogut na spirit nogut hia i lusim dispela pikinini na long dispela taim tasol, sik bilong em i pinis." refR="17.18" srcref="MAT 17.18"
MAT 18.4 Jisas kes pene, Ya tekispaij om aij aipisieiyn, pene om lin aktapala ke awko om antanom awkaꞌiw awko pene re pujelen welen, om lin kolon akwa olonma na kingdom iyn heven ono. Elin ektek.|src="CN01734B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="18.2" captionR="Jisas i tok, Mi tok tru long yupela, sapos yupela i no senis na kamap olsem ol liklik pikinini, yupela bai i no inap long go insait long kingdom bilong heven. Nogat tru." refR="18.2" srcref="MAT 18.4"
MAT 18.14 Niy tekniawtek re sipsip wa kouw enian sisip kawa kelek tawantan|src="GT00033.tif" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="18.12" captionR="Wasman i kisim bek wanpela sipsip i lus" refR="18.12" srcref="MAT 18.14"
MAT 19.13 Niy elen korꞌo re pujelen karama na Jisas iyn yi awtatawana re ke yi awꞌestek God iyn awo blesim re|src="CN01600B.tif" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="19.13" captionR="Sampela lain i kisim ol pikinini i kam long Jisas long putim han antap long ol na beten long God long blesim ol" refR="19.13" srcref="MAT 19.13"
MAT 19.16 Niy taako tekera Jisas pene, Tisa, ya mas awuo anen omon ke ya koluon awij laip tekmen pene peyian ono?|src="cn01773B.tif" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="19.16" captionR="Wanpela man i askim Jisas olsem, Tisa, mi mas mekim wanem gutpela samting na mi inap long kisim dispela laip i stap oltaim oltaim?" refR="19.16" srcref="MAT 19.16"
MAT 20.30 Niy entin talakuaro kotur ro karawaw nokuoteken ke teres Jisas pene, Niy Prum, ena Devit Onton Wuruaw, olom mas awtaiyn lot!|src="GT00034.tif" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="20.30" captionR="Tupela aipas man i singaut strong long Jisas na tok olsem, Bikpela, yu Pikinini bilong Devit, yu sori long mitupela!" refR="20.30" srcref="MAT 20.30"
MAT 21.9 Atawa aan iyn Devit Onton Wuruaw!|src="CN01782B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="21.9" captionR="Yumi litimapim nem bilong Pikinini bilong Devit!" refR="21.9" srcref="MAT 21.9"
MAT 21.13 Jisas kanat re niy terꞌeiyliw ke torum o temple olonma.|src="CN01787B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="21.13" captionR="Jisas i rausim ol lain i salim ol samting insait long tempel." refR="21.13" srcref="MAT 21.13"
MAT 21.42 At re kamda karꞌasna ke keres pene at aiwor ke korouw kerle ono, epin peyian ekmen pene at omon peyian iyn taknaipem ke tokouw olon.|src="GT00082.tif" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="21.42" captionR="Dispela ston ol kamda i ting olsem em ston nogut na ol i tromoi hia, bihain tru i kamap olsem nambawan ston bilong strongim banis bilong haus." refR="21.42" srcref="MAT 21.42"
MAT 22.21 Jisas tekes weyie re pene, Sopana ke om mas awkej o iyn Sisar ono awa yi ke o iyn God ono yipe awa yi antan.|src="cn01790B.tif" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="22.21" captionR="Jisas i bekim tok long ol olsem, Orait, olsem na yupela i mas givim ol samting bilong Sisar i go long em na ol samting bilong God i go long em yet." refR="22.21" srcref="MAT 22.21"
MAT 23.7 Re Farisi terter re muak teweiyn iyn terꞌestek|src="GT00035b.tif" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="23.7" captionR="Ol Farisi i save pasim bikpela paspas bilong prea" refR="23.5" srcref="MAT 23.7"
MAT 24.41 Niy temiyn entin armen armum plawa iyn artuiyn bret, ke God awouw taako awa ele taako ono awmen.|src="GT00037.tif" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="24.41" captionR="Tupela meri bai i stap wokim plaua bilong kukim bret, na God bai i kisim wanpela na larim narapela hia i stap bek." refR="24.41" srcref="MAT 24.41"
MAT 25.39 Tem aampia et teniaw e elim ko e o e kemin karabus ke et tama teniaw e?|src="CN02084B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="25.39" captionR="Wanem taim mipela lukim yu i gat sik o stap long kalabus na mipela i bin kam na lukim yu?" refR="25.39" srcref="MAT 25.39"
MAT 26.30 Ene tonuoiy yaꞌe iyn awo kontrak. Ya tektij tonuoiy ene iyn ya awuawpaij re o kokelek re temiyn wuruaw tartar iyn teriey ene toro re ono.|src="cn01804B.tif" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="26.28" captionR="Dispela em blut bilong mi bilong mekim kontrak. Mi kapsaitaim bilong mi bai rausim ol sin planti manmeri bilong dispela graun i bin mekim." refR="26.28" srcref="MAT 26.30"
MAT 26.41 Yi waweyiema na re disaipel yiꞌe ono enian ke keniaw pene re koron muoiyn konuiyn ono.|src="CN01811B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="26.40" captionR="Em i kam bek long ol disaipel bilong em na lukim olsem ol i slip pinis." refR="26.40" srcref="MAT 26.41"
MAT 26.51 Judas muliey Jisas.|src="cn01812B.tif" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="26.49" captionR="Judas i kis long Jisas." refR="26.49" srcref="MAT 26.51"
MAT 26.60 Re kerpiyljek re aij aiwor iyn awrotna Jisas ono iyn re arla yi awmat.|src="cn01815B.tif" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="26.59" captionR="Ol i painim ol tok giaman bilong kotim Jisas long ol i ken kilim em i dai." refR="26.59" srcref="MAT 26.60"
MAT 26.72 Pita kepip ke yi tekes re pene, Ya tekispaij om na Aan iyn Niy Prum, ya lin kuo sawe niy soana!|src="cn01819B.tiF" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="26.72" captionR="Pita i tok, Mi tok tru antap long yupela long nem bilong Bikpela, mi no save tru long dispela man!" refR="26.72" srcref="MAT 26.72"
MAT 27.18 Pailat tekera re pene, Om tekpiyl inan, Jisas Barabas ene o Jisas re terkiy Krais ene awa na om?|src="cn01825B.tif" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="27.17" captionR="Pailat i askim ol olsem, Yupela laikim bai husait, Jisas Barabas o dispela Jisas ol i kolim Krais, bai i go long yupela?" refR="27.17" srcref="MAT 27.18"
MAT 27.44 Niy uuntana taako koto kruse koto yi nakan palaw ke taako koto kruse koto yi nakan kais ono.|src="CN01841B.TIF" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="27.44" captionR="Wanpela man bilong pait na stil i stap long diwai kros long han sut na narapela i stap long diwai kros long han kais bilong em." refR="27.44" srcref="MAT 27.44"
MAT 27.53 Merꞌer peyian na tem soono, roiyn prum re teryiytekna tekmen tempel ono kompuot on entin, eyiat wa waꞌiw teken pet.|src="GT00041.tif" size="span" pgpos="t" ref="27.51" captionR="Stret long dispela taim, bikpela laplap i hangamap insait long tempel i bruk tupela hap, stat long antap na i go daun olgeta long daunbilo bilong en." refR="27.51" srcref="MAT 27.53"
MAT 27.66 Re kerle re ami ono karlaima matmat ono ke koron iyn kerniaw ektekna.|src="cn01848B.tif" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="27.66" captionR="Ol i putim ol ami raunim dispela matmat na ol i stap na was gut tru." refR="27.66" srcref="MAT 27.66"
MAT 28.7 Ensel kes pene Jisas usia enian ono pene aij yi kes ka.|src="cn01851B.tif" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="28.6" captionR="Ensel i tok, Jisas i kirap gen pinis olsem em i bin tok bipo." refR="28.6" srcref="MAT 28.7"
MAT 28.15 Re kerej re ami ono atawuan iyn re awres pene re disaipel iyn Jisasꞌe karama korouw yi karwa.|src="cn01858B.tif" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="28.13" captionR="Ol i givim mani long ol soldia long ol bai tok, ol lain bilong Jisas i stilim bodi bilong em." refR="28.13" srcref="MAT 28.15"
MAT 28.20 Tem re kerniaw yi, re kerꞌestek yi. Elinke elen reꞌe kerꞌep tingting entin na yi.|src="cn01882B.tif" size="span" pgpos="b" ref="28.20" captionR="Taim ol i lukim em, ol i lotu long em. Tasol sampela bilong ol i gat tupela tingting long en." refR="28.20" srcref="MAT 28.20"
